# Simple Telegram Ban Bot

## How to Run
Install and run
```bash
make
```
Install only
```bash
make deps
make configs
```

## How to use
It has two commands:
`/id` with reply message gets author id of the message
`/ban {time} {reason}` with reply message bans author of the message

### Time format
`1m` = 1 minute
`2h` = 2 hours
`3d` = 3 days
`4w` = 4 weeks
